sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User
participant HistoryApp as Commit History Webview
participant HistoryRouter as HistoryMessageRouter
participant Registry as RepositoryRegistry
participant UseCase as HistoryUseCases
participant Repository as GitRepository implements GitHistoryOperations
participant Runtime as HybridGitRuntime
participant Cli as CliGitRuntime

User->>HistoryApp: Open Commit History
HistoryApp->>HistoryRouter: history/dataRequest(repositoryLocator, PageRequest, filters, requestId)
HistoryRouter->>Registry: resolveRepository(repositoryLocator)
Registry-->>HistoryRouter: GitRepository
HistoryRouter->>UseCase: getCommitHistory(Repository, filters, PageRequest, signal)
UseCase->>Repository: getCommitGraph(filters, PageRequest, signal)
Repository->>Runtime: getCommitGraph(executionContext, filters, PageRequest, signal)
Runtime->>Cli: getCommitGraph(executionContext, filters, PageRequest, signal)
Cli-->>Runtime: Page(GitCommit)
Runtime-->>Repository: Page(GitCommit)
Repository-->>UseCase: Page(GitCommit)
UseCase-->>HistoryRouter: Page(CommitSummary)
HistoryRouter-->>HistoryApp: history/dataResponse(requestId, Page(CommitSummary))
HistoryApp-->>User: Render cursor page of commit history

User->>HistoryApp: Select commit
HistoryApp->>HistoryRouter: history/commitDetailsRequest(repositoryLocator, commitHash, requestId)
HistoryRouter->>Registry: resolveRepository(repositoryLocator)
Registry-->>HistoryRouter: GitRepository
HistoryRouter->>UseCase: getCommitDetails(Repository, commitHash, signal)
UseCase->>Repository: getCommitDetails(commitHash, signal)
Repository->>Runtime: getCommitDetails(executionContext, commitHash, signal)
Runtime->>Cli: getCommitDetails(executionContext, commitHash, signal)
Cli-->>Runtime: GitCommit details and file changes
Runtime-->>Repository: GitCommit details and file changes
Repository-->>UseCase: GitCommit details and file changes
UseCase-->>HistoryRouter: CommitDetails
HistoryRouter-->>HistoryApp: history/commitDetailsResponse(requestId, details)
HistoryApp-->>User: Render commit message and changed files

User->>HistoryApp: Load more
HistoryApp->>HistoryRouter: history/dataRequest(repositoryLocator, NextCursorPageRequest, filters, requestId)
HistoryRouter->>Registry: resolveRepository(repositoryLocator)
Registry-->>HistoryRouter: GitRepository
HistoryRouter->>UseCase: getCommitHistory(Repository, filters, NextCursorPageRequest, signal)
UseCase->>Repository: getCommitGraph(filters, NextCursorPageRequest, signal)
Repository->>Runtime: getCommitGraph(executionContext, filters, NextCursorPageRequest, signal)
Runtime->>Cli: getCommitGraph(executionContext, filters, NextCursorPageRequest, signal)
Cli-->>Runtime: Page(GitCommit)
Runtime-->>Repository: Page(GitCommit)
Repository-->>UseCase: Page(GitCommit)
UseCase-->>HistoryRouter: Page(CommitSummary)
HistoryRouter-->>HistoryApp: history/dataResponse(requestId, Page(CommitSummary))
HistoryApp-->>User: Append next cursor page
